{
  "text": "Promastigotes treated with H. leucospilota extracts (IC 50 ) were tested to perceive morphological changes. Promastigotes were centrifuged for 10 min at 1000 g and supernatant was removed carefully and the sediments were suspended in PBS. Morphological alteration was studied after treatment under light microscope on the magnification of \u00d7100 at different time points from 0 to 72 hours [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
